    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a mirror-like finish with no scratches, dents, or chips. Inside, the cabin remains pristine, with leather that feels factory-new and every electronic component functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been meticulously stored and maintained to the highest standards. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality example that will satisfy even the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 49000.0,
